    Memo's original definition in the XDR file is: 
     union Memo switch (MemoType type)
 {
 case MEMO_NONE:
     void;
 case MEMO_TEXT:
     string text<28>;
 case MEMO_ID:
     uint64 id;
 case MEMO_HASH:
     Hash hash; // the hash of what to pull from the content server
 case MEMO_RETURN:
     Hash retHash; // the hash of the tx you are rejecting
 };
